---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Manmeet Kaur">
	<main>
		<section class="about-header">
			<h1>About Manmeet Kaur</h1>
		</section>

		<section class="about-content">
			<div class="profile">
				<div class="profile-text">
					<h2>Education & Credentials</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>Pursuing Ph.D. in Cognitive Neuroscience, IIT Bombay</li>
						<li>Licensed Clinical Psychologist (RCI Registered)</li>
						<li>NET-JRF Qualified</li>
						<li>4 Years of Clinical Experience</li>
						<li>Certified in Basics of Addiction Management</li>
						<li>Certified in Rational Emotive Behavior Therapy (REBT)</li>

					</ul>

					<h2>My Approach</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>Person-Centered and Collaborative Approach: I prioritize creating a safe, empathetic, and non-judgmental environment to foster trust and rapport. My approach is client-centered, ensuring that your unique needs and goals guide the therapeutic process.</li>
						<li>Comprehensive Initial Assessment: In the initial sessions, I focus on understanding your history, exploring your concerns, and clarifying your expectations. Together, we define long-term and short-term goals tailored to your individual circumstances.</li>
						<li>Evidence-Based Interventions: Utilizing evidence-based therapeutic techniques, I help you explore and work on your thoughts, behaviors, and emotions. My aim is to empower you with tools and strategies to overcome challenges and achieve personal growth.</li>
						<li>Holistic and Adaptive Therapy: I adapt my interventions to address a wide range of issues, such as anxiety, depression, trauma, and stress management, while ensuring a holistic focus on your well-being.</li>
						<li>In-Depth Assessments: To gain a deeper understanding of your symptoms and personality, I utilize evidence-based assessment tools, including personality tests, projective tests, rating scales, and other diagnostic measures. These tools provide valuable insights to inform the therapeutic process.</li>
					</ul>

					<h2>Areas of Expertise</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>Anxiety and Depression</li>
						<li>Trauma and PTSD</li>
						<li>Relationship Issues</li>
						<li>Life Transitions</li>
						<li>Stress Management</li>
						<li>Substance Use</li>
						<li>ADHD and Autism</li>
						<li>Anger Management</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about-header {
		background: #B3A08F;
		color: white;
		padding: 8rem 2rem;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.about-header h1 {
		color: white;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.about-content {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
	}
	.profile {
		display: grid;
		gap: 2rem;
	}
	.profile-text h2 {
		margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;
	}
	.profile-text h2:first-child {
		margin-top: 0;
	}
	.profile-text p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	.profile-text ul {
		list-style-position: inside;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	.profile-text li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
</style>